                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">You didn't mention Zevfeer's Bite, a Shadow Knight spell that does 200 hp damage to its target and gives 100 mana (slot 8) and 200 health to all members of the knight's group that are in range (100).
<br />

<br />
Druids and Rangers can cast Mask of the Hunter and Mask of the Stalker, which gives them 3 mana/tick (slot 3).  Druids can also cast Mask of the Forest which is an upgrade that gives them 4 mana/tick.
<br />

<br />
Magicians can cast Xegony's Phantasmal Guard which is 8 mana/tick (slot 4).  They can cast Elemental Siphon on their pet which does damage to their pet but gives them another 5 mana/tick (slot 7).
<br />

<br />
Necromancers can cast Seduction of Saryrn which gives them 50 mana/tick (slot 2).  Lucy also has Ancient: Seduction of Chaos which is an upgrade that gives them 60 mana/tick.  Yikes!
<br />

<br />
Paladins can cast Aura of the Crusader, a self buff that gives them 4 mana/tick (slot 3).
<br />

<br />
Shaman can cannibalize with Cannibalize 4 (82 mana as often as it refreshes and they have health) and-or their Cannibalization AA (1066 mana as it refreshes and they have health).
<br />

<br />
You mentioned it for Bards, but all hybrids can get the Body and Mind Rejuvenation AA that gives them an extra mana/tick regen (Natural Healing 3 and Mental Clarity 3 as prerequisites).
<br />

<br />
Clerics can cast Yaulp VI, which is unusual in that it gives them 12 mana/tick but only if they are not on a horse or meditating (sitting).  Their Armor of the Zealot buff (8 mana/tick, slot 4) does not stack with Blessing of the Nine but does stack with Virtue.
<br />

<br />
Also, I think it's worth mentioning our Gather Mana AA.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=824212" target="_blank" class="postlink">Visionary Provender</a>, High Elf Coercer (retired)
<br />
<a href="http://www.therunes.net/forums/viewtopic.php?p=18979" target="_blank" class="postlink">E67.154/TT h+ 2.9khp 4.8km ft12 !G&gt;&lt;3 e++(+++) o++ T+++ L++ H++(+++) f- g+ b- c++(+++) t+ D- !X</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
