                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Yes, the 25 from meditating with 250 med skill stacks with all other forms of regen, including natural. According to bards who know a lot more about natural mana regen than us, you regen 3 per tick standing at 65 without any AAs, and 1 per tick standing at all other levels. MC3 goes on top of that.
<br />

<br />
So if you are 65 with MC3 and 250 med skill, you regen 31 mana "naturally" while medding.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
