                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Update to the bard stuff:  The mana component of our songs is not modified by instrument mods (healing component is).
<br />

<br />
Bards will only benefit from:  MC (4 Max), FT (15 Max), and Meditate (Skill capped at 1). No other spells / songs will increase our mana regen.  Bards who ask for KEI usually want it to increase mana pool to allow for more fades.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
